name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of punks are assigned a mysterious mission. These punks are very deadly. They have their own superpowers. Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center. For now, the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #008
Male


Name         : Goerian 
Strength     : 100/100
Intelligence : 100/100


Goerian was a soldier who was killed in the battle against the monster orkhis and its army.
The five sages of the mountain of Kupparnaf brought him back to life and gave him a part of their powers.
